title: She called CNN reporter 'liberal hack' after question ... then Fox host asked
description: Fox News host Laura Ingraham asks Sen. Martha McSally (R-AZ) about wanting witnesses in the Senate impeachment trial.

title: Disney is renaming '20th Century Fox'
description: 20th Century Fox is an icon of Hollywood history. Its epic fanfare title card has appeared in front of "The Sound of Music," "Star Wars" and other major films over the past 85 years. But in 2020, that name is no more.

title: Boeing discovers issue with 737 Max flight computers, source says
description: Boeing's troubled 737 Max has run into a new glitch.

title: What the royal 'deal' will look like for Prince Harry and Meghan
description: With the surprise decision by the Duke and Duchess of Sussex to step back from royal life, CNN's Max Foster asks what the future holds for the British royal family.

title: Lewinsky offers colorful remark after Trump move
description: The announcement that former independent counsel Ken Starr is joining President Donald Trump's impeachment defense team surprised many on Friday, but one person, apparently, had an especially notable reaction to the news.

title: German Shepard gives birth to green puppy
description: Shana Stamey said she was "freaking out" when she saw her white German Shepherd give birth to a green puppy. The color was caused by meconium, an infant's earlier stool, which the puppy encountered before birth and is temporary, according to veterinarian Suzanne Cianciulli. CNN affiliate WLOS reports.

title: Why South Koreans are flipping out over a US ambassador's mustache
description: It might just be the most bizarre criticism of a US ambassador in recent memory.

title: Tiger Woods' son is good at golf, but video poses wider questions
description: The genie is out of the bottle. Tiger Woods' son Charlie plays golf and his swing looks sweet.

title: Fires subside but floods cause chaos in Australia
description: The storms are bringing some relief to firefighters battling historic wildfires in Australia but the rain has also caused flooding in several areas due to the dry ground.

title: From voter questions to walk-up songs and selfies, this is every campaign rally
description: From tough voter questions to walk-up songs to selfie lines, CNN's political embeds are paid to capture the behind-the-scenes moments that matter in the 2020 presidential race. See them all in CNN's new series "On The Road."

title: There are now four $1 trillion companies

title: Louis Vuitton just bought the world's second-biggest diamond
description: Louis Vuitton has just bought the world's second-largest diamond, another sign of the French brand's ambitions in the luxury jewelry market.

title: He nearly died hang gliding. Then he did this...
description: Chris Gurksy nearly died hang gliding. No, that's not an exaggeration. There's a viral video to prove it.
